test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7d7a64625a80>([-18])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7d7a64625a80> = [[1, -18], [1, -18, 1], [-18, 1, -18, 1, -18, 1], [-18, 1], [1, -18], [1, -18, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 34012224 == -18
 +  where 34012224 = <built-in function prod>([-18, -1, -2, -3, -6, -9, ...])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
